5021">请参阅此处</a>，了解如何在家中通过 BBC iPlayer 和其他地方观看音乐节（如果您无法观看）确保获得门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred Again..</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam Gallagher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">Catfish And The Bottlemen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gerry-cinnamon">Gerry Cinnamon</a>是今年音乐节的六大主角。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">雷伊</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">,</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c"> </a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">Spiritbox</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/renee-rapp">Reneé Rapp</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pendulum">Pendulum</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/denzel-curry">Denzel Curry</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kenny-beats">Kenny Beats</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nia-archives">Nia Archives</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/two-door-cinema-club">Two Door Cinema Club</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Neck-Deep">Neck Deep</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-chinouriri">Rachel Chinouriri</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hak-baker">Hak Baker</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a>等也预计将出演。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024"><i>请返回 NME，</i></a><i>了解雷丁和利兹 2024 的最新新闻、评论、采访、照片等。</i></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/leeds-festival-2024-jorja-smith-ashnikko-added-back-to-line-up-after-bbc-radio-1-stage-closure-3786568">2024 年利兹音乐节后：BBC Radio 1 舞台关闭后，Jorja Smith 和 Ashnikko 重新回到阵容，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
